{"tid":1885883,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"未subscribe周庭同我入晒嚟","createTime":"2020-02-18T14:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T15:12:12.000Z","uid":229510,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"44a80bd8da20c4c660e9818584a981e8ebf2f682","tid":1885883,"uid":229510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:50:56.000Z","msg":"（日本語うしろ）<br />\n<br />\n黃Youtuber已經係咁被人黃標, 快啲幫下手, 周庭姐姐就快七萬訂閣喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每日推<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">周庭</span></strong></span>姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到超越大J成為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港第一</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n周庭姐姐今日無新片<br />\n<br />\n周庭姐姐最新影片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Zde3pAYVSek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZde3pAYVSek&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=3a91d94b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Zde3pAYVSek</a><br />\n<br />\n周庭姐姐<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>YouTube</strong></span> channel:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYstQdiN4QR-EgclyZ4IDfQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCYstQdiN4QR-EgclyZ4IDfQ&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=d5b0d196\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYstQdiN4QR-EgclyZ4IDfQ</a><br />\n<br />\n周庭姐姐<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>Twitter</strong></span></span>:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chowtingagnes?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http